    "long_instructions": "### DJ Darkness needs a short loop\r\nDJ Darkness loves this heavy beat and ambient sounds. She is having trouble live coding fast enough for anything new to happen in the first 8 measures. Code a small loop that she can trigger early in the song that she can play while she live codes another part of the song.\r\n\r\nDo This:\r\n- Code an 6-measure loop that fits the beat.\r\n- Set it to trigger `at the next measure`.\r\n- Try triggering your new loop to play at Measure 2.\r\n\r\n",
